point A at (100, 80)
point B at (300, 80)
point C at (200, 280)
triangle T of A B C

segment AB of A B
segment BC of B C
segment AC of A C

midpoint Mab of AB
midpoint Mbc of BC
midpoint Mac of AC
triangle Medial of Mab Mbc Mac

circumcircle CC of T
incircle IC of T

label Medial "Medial Triangle"
label CC "Circumcircle"
label IC "Incircle"